Association analysis

pd_h2 <- function(R2O, case_prop, prevalence = 0.22) {
  K <- prevalence
  P <- case_prop
  thd <- -1 * qnorm(K, 0, 1)
  zv <- dnorm(thd) # z (normal density)
  mv <- zv / K # mean liability for case
  theta <- mv * (P - K) / (1 - K) * (mv * (P - K) / (1 - K) - thd) #  in equation
  cv <- K * (1 - K) / zv^2 * K * (1 - K) / (P * (1 - P)) # C in
  return(R2O * cv / (1 + R2O * theta * cv))
}

methylation pcs

library(RSpectra)
compute_pcs <- function(A, k = 10) {
  n <- nrow(A)
  p <- ncol(A)
  A <- scale(A, center = TRUE, scale = FALSE)
  s <- svds(A, k, nu = 0, nv = k)
  j <- seq_len(k)
  s$d <- s$d / sqrt(max(1, n - 1))

  dimnames(s$v) <- list(colnames(A), paste0("PC", j))
  r <- list(sdev = s$d, rotation = s$v)
  class(r) <- "prcomp"
  r
}
res <- compute_pcs(betas_sub)
PCs <- res$rotation

S4_to_dataframe <- function(s4obj) {
  nms <- slotNames(s4obj)

  lst <- lapply(nms, function(nm) slot(s4obj, nm))
  as.data.frame(setNames(lst, nms))
}

get_dmr_effects <- function(dmr, limma_res) {
  dmr_coord <- str_match_all(as.character(dmr), "(chr.*):([0-9]*)-([0-9]*)")[[1]]
  cpgs <- annotation[annotation$chr == dmr_coord[2] & annotation$pos >= as.numeric(dmr_coord[3]) & annotation$pos <= as.numeric(dmr_coord[4]), ]
  res <- cbind(cpgs, limma_res[cpgs$Name, ])
  dmr_1 <- as.data.frame(res[!is.na(res$logFC), ])
  dmr_methy <- melt(lumi::m2beta(betas_sub[dmr_1$Name, na_row]), stringsAsFactors = FALSE)
  to_plot <- merge(dmr_1, dmr_methy, by.x = "Name", by.y = "Var1")
  to_plot$DMR <- dmr
  merge(to_plot, all_data, by.x = "Var2", by.y = "patient")
}
get_dmr_res <- function(dmr, limma_res) {
  dmr_coord <- str_match_all(as.character(dmr), "(chr.*):([0-9]*)-([0-9]*)")[[1]]
  cpgs <- annotation[annotation$chr == dmr_coord[2] & annotation$pos >= as.numeric(dmr_coord[3]) & annotation$pos <= as.numeric(dmr_coord[4]), ]
  res <- cbind(cpgs, limma_res[cpgs$Name, ])
  res$DMR <- dmr
  return(res)
}
plot_dmrs <- function(dmr_res, limma_res, case_control) {
  to_plot <- rbindlist(lapply(dmr_res$coord, function(dmr) get_dmr_effects(dmr, limma_res)))

  p1 <- ggplot(to_plot %>% mutate(SCORE1_AVG = scale(SCORE1_AVG)), aes(pos, value, color = SCORE1_AVG)) +
    geom_point() +
    scale_color_gradient(low = rev(case_control)[1], high = rev(case_control)[2]) +
    facet_wrap(~DMR, scales = "free", nrow = 1) +
    theme_minimal() +
    labs(color = "Normalized PD PRS")
  p2 <- ggplot(to_plot %>% mutate(PD = ifelse(PD == 1, "CASE", "CONTROL")), aes(factor(pos), value, color = PD)) +
    geom_boxplot(position = position_dodge(0.75)) +
    scale_color_manual(values = case_control) +
    facet_wrap(~DMR, scales = "free", nrow = 1) +
    theme_minimal() +
    stat_summary(aes(group = PD), fun = mean, geom = "line") +
    labs(color = "PD status") +
    theme(axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 90))
  print(p1)
  print(p2)
}

Permutation test for checking if reason for discrepancy between cases and controls is sample sized

library(parallel)
num_control <- sum(control_select)
num_cases <- sum(case_select)

run_at_sample_size <- function(size) {
  to_select <- sample((1:length(na_row))[na_row], size)
  design_prs <- model.matrix(~ 1 + SCORE1_AVG + age + plate + sex + V3 + V4 + V5 + PC1 + PC2 + PC3 + PC4 + PC5 + PC6 + PC7 + PC8 + PC9 + PC10, data = reg_all_data[to_select, ])
  prs_fit <- lmFit(betas_sub[, to_select], design_prs)
  prs_fit <- eBayes(prs_fit)
  topTable(prs_fit, coef = 2, number = Inf)
}


run_at_sample_size_control <- function(size) {
  to_select <- sample((1:length(na_row))[control_select], size)
  design_prs <- model.matrix(~ 1 + SCORE1_AVG + age + plate + sex + V3 + V4 + V5 + PC1 + PC2 + PC3 + PC4 + PC5 + PC6 + PC7 + PC8 + PC9 + PC10, data = reg_all_data[to_select, ])
  prs_fit <- lmFit(betas_sub[, to_select], design_prs)
  prs_fit <- eBayes(prs_fit)
  topTable(prs_fit, coef = 2, number = Inf)
}

res_control_size <- mclapply(1:10, function(x) run_at_sample_size(num_control), mc.cores = 10)
res_case_size <- mclapply(1:10, function(x) run_at_sample_size(num_cases), mc.cores = 10)

res_case_size_control <- mclapply(1:10, function(x) run_at_sample_size_control(num_cases), mc.cores = 10)

control_hits <- unlist(lapply(res_control_size, function(x) nrow(subset(x, adj.P.Val < 0.05 & abs(logFC) > 0.03))))

case_hits <- unlist(lapply(res_case_size, function(x) nrow(subset(x, adj.P.Val < 0.05 & abs(logFC) > 0.03))))
case_size_control_hits <- unlist(lapply(res_case_size_control, function(x) nrow(subset(x, adj.P.Val < 0.05 & abs(logFC) > 0.03))))
df <- data.frame(hits = c(mean(case_hits), mean(control_hits)), sample_size = c("Sampled to |Cases|", "Sampled to |Controls|"), dev = c(sd(case_hits), sd(control_hits)))

write_results <- function(prs_res, prs_dmr, label) {
  prs_res %>%
    rownames_to_column("probe") %>%
    filter(adj.P.Val < 0.25) %>%
    left_join(annot %>% select(Name, CHR, UCSC_RefGene_Name, Relation_to_UCSC_CpG_Island, MAPINFO), by = c("probe" = "Name")) %>%
    mutate(gene = gsub(";.*", "", UCSC_RefGene_Name)) %>%
    mutate(gene = ifelse(gene == "", probe, gene)) %>%
    write.csv(glue("{label}prs_res_fdr025_mval.csv"), row.names = F, quote = F)

  rbindlist(lapply(prs_dmr$coord, function(dmr) as.data.frame(get_dmr_res(dmr, prs_res)))) %>%
    left_join(prs_dmr, by = c("DMR" = "coord")) %>%
    write.csv(glue("{label}PRS_DMR_CPGs_mval.csv"), row.names = F, quote = F)
}
write_results(prs_res, prs_dmr, "cross-sex_")
write_results(male_res, male_prs_dmr, "male_")
write_results(female_res, female_prs_dmr, "female_")

summary(fit1_null)
nagelkerke(fit1, null = fit1_null)
lin1 <- lm(PD_fixed ~ SCORE1_AVG + sex + PC1 + PC2 + PC3, data = all_digpd_data)
lin2 <- lm(PD_fixed ~ sex + PC1 + PC2 + PC3, data = all_digpd_data)
R2 <- (deviance(lin2) - deviance(lin1)) / deviance(lin2)
h2 <- pd_h2(R2, sum(all_digpd_data$PD_fixed) / nrow(all_digpd_data), 0.01)
